comment: * A listener interface, which will be notified on foreground service state changes.

methods.name: void onForegroundServiceStateChanged(String packageName, int uid, int pid, boolean started)
methods.comment:
* Call when the given process's foreground service state changes.
         *
         * @param packageName The package name of the process.
         * @param uid The UID of the process.
         * @param pid The pid of the process.
         * @param started {@code true} if the process transits from non-FGS state to FGS state.

methods.name: void onForegroundServiceNotificationUpdated(String packageName, int uid, int foregroundId, boolean canceling)
methods.comment:
* Call when the notification of the foreground service is updated.
         *
         * @param packageName The package name of the process.
         * @param uid The UID of the process.
         * @param foregroundId The current foreground service notification ID.
         * @param canceling The given notification is being canceled.

methodNames: void onForegroundServiceStateChanged(String packageName, int uid, int pid, boolean started)
void onForegroundServiceNotificationUpdated(String packageName, int uid, int foregroundId, boolean canceling)
